{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "两位造物主 第21章 5-3 “父子”的对话",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "一行人成功阻止了圣域龙，\\n却因圣树的崩塌\\n和法尔艾斯的攻击而走散。\\n亚斯拉姆与法尔艾斯对峙时\\n看穿了其真实身份乃起始之人。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "伊莉雅，小心身后。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "啊，嗯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "那个，塞西娅，\\n你不会是“看不见”吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你从刚才开始就在用目视以外的\\n方法判断敌人的攻击吧？\\n凭视觉不可能如此快速判断。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "不愧是伊莉雅，瞒不过你呢。\\n这应该也是契约的影响。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我也不清楚是因为我的身体\\n跟不上巴哈姆特的力量，\\n还是我为这份力量付出的代价……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "不过要是只有这点代价，\\n已经很便宜我了。而且……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "伊莉雅，小心头顶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我现在比目视的时候看得更清楚。\\n直觉像经过磨砺的针一般敏锐……\\n敏锐到让我有些害怕。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你没事吧？后悔了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "这份力量很强大……\\n我不知道能不能驾驭它，\\n所以有些害怕。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "但我不后悔这一选择。\\n我现在只想向前看。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我知道了……\\n那就先打倒这家伙吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "好！胜利在望了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "看来总算是让圣域龙\\n消停了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100054_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "哈啊、哈啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "塞西娅，你的模样变了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "毕竟用的是巴哈姆特的力量，\\n就算只有一半，\\n她的身体也到极限了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "似乎是这样。只要体力恢复了，\\n我应该还能借用这份力量……\\n啊……视觉也恢复了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "太好了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "真是够了！这回又是什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "圣树好像快崩塌了……\\n是受黑暗魔力的影响吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "待在这里会被活埋的。\\n大家赶紧下树！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "呀啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "塞西娅！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "哥哥……我可以去会会\\n那个空壳王子吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "倒是无妨，\\n不过你找他有什么事吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "我想问问他，真相摆在眼前，\\n他是怎么想的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "怎么办！\\n塞西娅她们掉下去了！\\n要赶紧救她们……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "冷静点，只要下了树\\n应该就能跟她们会合。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "先从这里脱身，然后下树。\\n这才是我们该做的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "知道了！那……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "你以为你们想走就能走吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "果然如我所料……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "这里就交给我吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "既然他要留下，我就来帮他吧。\\n我猜……我应该是\\n最熟悉他战斗方式的人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "迦道夫？\\n为什么说你最熟悉……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "看来没时间犹豫了，\\n真的可以拜托你吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "嗯，多少让我帮点忙吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "谢斯，巴尔库斯，\\n你们要保重啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "你果然是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "好了，快走吧！\\n席菈就交给你们了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07",
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "嗯。我们走吧，席菈！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "芩罗达，奈迪犹，\\n你们不撤吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01",
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这家伙会成为\\n我与巴哈姆特之间的障碍。\\n要在这里解决掉他。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "呵呵，好啊。\\n那我就奉陪吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "好凌厉的攻势，不愧是父王。\\n啊失礼了，现在您自称\\n是亚斯拉姆吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "你……不是法尔艾斯吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "你放塞西娅去异界，\\n还能认出不受因果桎梏的我\\n就是亚罗拉斯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "你就是“起始之人”吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "没错……\\n果然骗不过父王的眼睛啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "我儿子呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "这具身躯的主人，\\n也就是你儿子……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "已经死了。\\n因为龙鳞病一命呜呼。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "他一直都害怕死亡。渐渐地，\\n他终于找到了一个方法——\\n并不会完全死去的方法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "那就是唤醒“起始之人”。\\n不过我倒是没想到\\n竟然是人类解开了封印。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "他死后，我接管了他的肉体。\\n人死但躯体尚在，\\n也算是你儿子得偿所愿了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我相当中意这具身躯。\\n毕竟龙鳞病让他\\n比一般人类更结实。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "你这混蛋！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "哎呀，真不解风情。\\n难得父子团聚呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我没道理配合你胡闹。\\n“起始之人”，受死吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "你体内只寄宿了巴哈姆特\\n一半的力量，能奈我何？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你自己也不是完全形态吧，\\n毕竟复活条件尚未齐全。\\n在那之前解决掉你就是最好的办法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_09_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
